    video compression
    ^0HfIiZ8S

    video
    multiple frames ^eWYUkycM

    each frame one image ^21l7UNuy

    image compression ^cC6LxZ2y

    jpeg
    joint photographic experts group ^B1XHjNXp

    mpeg
    moving picture experts group ^RrGQycCJ

    jpeg image compression
    grey scale image 8 bits
    ^lHq1SXVd

    grey scale pic divided into blocks of 8X8 pixels ^7l01PKsp

    • jpeg changes pictures into vector
    • redundancies can be removed by compression method
      ^aC2Qw0Ez

    DCT: Discrete cosine transform
    changes 64 values so that relative relationship are kept but redundencies are revealed ^XQPWmDXs

    Quantization :
    - reduce no of bits needed for encoding
    - divide the no. by some constant and remove the fraction
    - loss some info here
    - therefore jpeg is lossy ^bynrQs3f

    redundant zero are removed ^92GzKd85

    Image Compression : jpeg
    ^1GxbQalo

    video compression : Mpeg ^0zbfqpiP

    • compressing set of frames
    • spatial compression of each frame with jpeg
    • temporal compression redundant frames are removed
    • tv 50 frames per sec
    • eg: when someone talking most of the frame are same except for the segment of frame around lips ^Kl3pyHXb

    mpeg ^0l1Andvy

    i-frames ^n87ePRfM

    p-frames ^yNfFzZFa

    b-frames ^Mh3x0mvj

    Streaming stored audio/video

    ^lJ8iUOFN

    using web server ^Gpnmm781

    media server and RTS ^1lArZPX8

    web server with metafile ^H6tmpO7Z

    media server ^kP9QXM2b

    drawback :
    audio / video large even after compression
    - video played only after complete video download

    ^dAarHKwW

    both media player and browser are using http which designed to run over tcp
    - tcp not appropriate for audio / vedio
    - ver web server designed for TCP ^Pe44gwtN

    • media player use URL in the metafile
    • downloading of audio/video from media server
      using udp

    ^R92qjzax

    • real time streaming protocol
    • control protocol
    • add more functionalities, playing of audio/video
    • out-of-band protocol (similar second to ftp) ^s3gNw0a2

    Realtime Interactive audio/video

    ^fmtIE84B

    video conferencing communicate visually and orally ^9U5eFOkp

    characteristics
    - time relationship :packets arrive in delays cause jitter
    - timestamp :
    - playback buffer
    - ordering
    - multicasting
    - translation high-bandwdith to lower-bandwidth
    - mixing - traffic made from mutiple streams ^wGqAhGhv

    Tcp not suitted for interactive traffic
    ^MX30AtzB

    RTP(real-time transport protocol)
    - handle real time traffic on internet
    - stands b/w udp and application program
    - provide time-stamping, sequencing, mixing facilities
    - encapsulated in udp
    - use even number port
    - allows flow of data
    ^xHq4HLbA

    RTP packet header format ^B6upLS2q

    payload
    31-H.261
    32 - mpeg2 video
    33-mpeg2 vedio ^6XYQA6YK

    2
    ^tG13wpTG

    1 ^lXNDl2UV

    1 ^GAJ8AiJt

    4bit ^NlbYl5et

    1 ^Eqa3Uuz9

    7 bit ^SmbksoJs

    16 bit ^A7Sb310k

    32 bit ^ddqcvoo3

    32 bit ^8lTGQiaQ

    32 bit ^jcq0KIzC

    32 bit ^fJEtHYPv

    32 bit ^F7VQiqHA

    RTCP
    - contol flow and quality of data
    - recipient send feedback to sources or sources
    - ^wNggt420

    sender report ^QM2n8gge

    receiver report
    ^CuiGkIrV

    Source Description Message ^ufotQ6bT

    Bye Message ^11DPHyAa

    Application specific message ^g23c1eti

    SIP(session intercation protocol)
    - session Initiation protocol
    - app layer protocol
    - establish , manage , terminates a multi media session call
    - used to create two party, multiparty, multicastparty
    - independent of protocol udp, tcp, sctp
    - ipaddress, emailaddress, phonenumber indentify sender and reciver

    ^9edQhtjX

    invite ^s61etckJ

    Ack ^6HzxoXHB

    bye ^ji8mezcj

    options ^iXqN1a2r

    cancel ^Agld8PXU

    register ^ir2CaZg5

    Messages ^dNyW7hY8

    establishing : 3 way handshake
    ^XcGxd7Hr

    caller: INVITE
    callee: reply
    caller: ack
    ^aiBS2bmH

    connection

    terminating : BYE ^cHYU3o2R

    SIP ^hpFbpbwe

    H.323 ^jy7RXAd8

    • standard designed by ITU to allow telephones ^Sk2mIY2t
